    "body" : "<p>You can enable pretty-printing by setting the <code>SerializationFeature.INDENT_OUTPUT</code> on your <code>ObjectMapper</code> like so:</p>\n\n<pre><code>mapper.enable(SerializationFeature.INDENT_OUTPUT);\n</code></pre>\n"
