    "question_id" : 17617370,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>The jackson API has changed:</p>\n\n<pre><code>new ObjectMapper()\n.writer()\n.withDefaultPrettyPrinter()\n.writeValueAsString(new HashMap&lt;String, Object&gt;());\n</code></pre>\n"
